      "description": "Looking for your next project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to get on the road at a rock-bottom price. Perfect for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for a diamond in the rough!",
