      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom character. Mechanically sound and aesthetically flawless, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the uncompromising quality of this investment-grade motorcar.",
