      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a deep, mirror-like exterior finish entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury; the premium leather seats are supple with no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and the original high-gloss trim remains flawless. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous manufacturer-spec maintenance schedule with all records included. Every button, sensor, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. From the whisper-quiet idle to the effortless acceleration, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model.",
      "price": 46500.0,
